🦴  High Speed Data Acquisition System Market Outlook Report 2025-2034 | Modular Systems and Real-Time Analytics Drive Growth - National Instruments Unveils PXIe-1092, Advancing High-Speed Data Throughput

Source: GlobeNewswire

The high-speed data acquisition market will reach $7.7 billion by 2032, growing from $4.5 billion in 2024. A 7.02% CAGR is predicted for the market, fueled by Industry 4.0 and R&D investments. Modular systems and real-time analytics will drive growth within this expanding data acquisition market.

🦴  Are Data Marketplaces the Future of AI?

Source: Dataversity.net

Data marketplaces address AI's hunger for data, streamlining dataset acquisition previously marked by silos. These marketplaces are reshaping AI model building by offering diverse and readily available datasets. For startups, leveraging data marketplaces can accelerate AI development and improve model accuracy while reducing acquisition costs.

🦴  Data Brokers are Selling Your Flight Information to CBP and ICE

Source: EFF

Data brokers exploit privacy gaps, selling precise location data, without consent, for profit. They supply CBP and ICE with flight data, bypassing warrant requirements in many cases. This impacts user privacy, raising ethical concerns about data collection and sale.

🦴  The Data ( Use and Access ) Act | Mayer Brown

Source: jdsupra.com

The Data Use and Access Act (DUAA) may standardize data access and use, fostering innovation particularly for health information. DUAA could preempt inconsistent state laws, creating a uniform federal framework for data practices nationwide. The Act aims to balance data access with privacy, mandating de-identification and security measures to mitigate risks, as seen in other frameworks.

🦴  What is data orchestration?

Source: Techtarget.com

Data orchestration automates and coordinates data movement across an enterprise using BI and analytical tools. It reduces data silos and improves data quality, potentially saving 20% on costs. Proper orchestration can enable real-time analytics, accelerating business insights by up to 30%.

🦴  Ministry plans automated data exchange to optimize tax revenue

Source: Antaranews.com
